---
title: Easy Cottage Pie with Cheesy Cheddar Mashed Potatoes
description: This classic casserole combines saucy beef filling and extra cheesy cheddar mashed potatoes. Broiling for the last few minutes gives this cottage pie a delicious golden crust.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pate-chinois-aux-petits-pois-5be507aa.jpg
